## Third-Party Dependencies

This software makes use of the following third-party libraries:

### SFML (Simple and Fast Multimedia Library)
- **License**: zlib/png License
- **Website**: https://www.sfml-dev.org/
- **Used for**: GUI rendering and window management
- **Optional**: Required only for GUI mode; software works without it

The SFML license is compatible with the MIT license and allows for both
commercial and non-commercial use.

### Standard C++ Library
- **License**: Implementation-specific (typically permissive)
- **Used for**: Core functionality, containers, algorithms
- **Required**: Yes (part of C++17 standard)

